name: Latent Timespace No.2: The Interstellar Wind
description:
Maybe there is no sound in astrospace, but the space will never be silent, because the interstellar wind carries various particles and energies crossing the whole space-time, bringing the secrets of the universe. The secret may be the poem of Hai Zi, " the wind far from is farther than the far place”, or perhaps the mystery of the birth of life in star clusters.

Introduction of the series: Latent Timespace, is the invisible higher dimensional space-time. The three-dimensional universe we currently see may only be a drop in the universe ocean. This series aims to reveal the knowable or unknowable sceneries in parallel universe with the help of artificial intelligence (AI), expanding the boundaries of vision that were normally limited in three dimensions.

隐时空2：元素之风

太空或许是无声的，但绝不是寂静的，因为星际之风会裹挟着各种元素粒子和能量，划过整个时空，顺便捎带来宇宙的秘密，这个秘密或许是海子的诗：“远在远方的风比远方更远”，或许是生命在星团中诞生的秘密。

系列说明: 隐时空，即不可见的高维时空；我们目前所见的三维宇宙，或许只是沧海一粟；本系列旨在借助人工智能(AI)技术，揭示平行时空中的可知或不可知，拓展原本被禁锢在三维中的视域界限。
